name: wtp manga cover pretrained
author: umzi-x-dead
description:
Purpose: pre-workout to speed up your workouts

While experimenting with color models for cugan, I just ran into problems that the official models are not imported correctly and have additional processing in addition to resizing. As a result, for my project I trained 2 x cugans for neosr; only resizing losses were applied to the dataset `(“lanczos”, “bicubic”, “bilenear”, “HAMMING”, “NEAREST”)`
dataset: custom dataset of manga covers and color manga in equal quality with pixiv
